                  <msContents>
                      <summary/>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                          <locus from="9" to="20"/>
                          <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4935Kaleb">History of King Kāleb</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#9"/>
                              በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘቦቱ፡ ክሂል። 
                              መጽሐፈ፡ ዜና፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ዘአስተጋብኦ፡ ወፈከሮ፡ አረጋዊ፡ በላምባራስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ጽርዓዊ፡ እምልሳነ፡ ጽርዕ፡ ኀበ፡ ልሳነ፡ አምኃራ። 
                              ወዘሜጦስ፡ እምልሳነ፡ አምኃራ፡ ኀበ፡ ልሳነ፡ ግዕዝ፡ ማእምር፡ አርቶዶክሳዊ፡ ዘይሰመይ፡ ነጋሽ። ወሀገሩኒ፡ ማኅደረ፡ ማርያም።
                          </incipit>
                          <note>According to the incipit, the text was translated from Greek into Amharic by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4700Giyorgis">
                           <roleName type="title">bālāmbārās</roleName> Giyorgis</persName>, 
                              and translated from Amharic into Gǝʿǝz by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12006Nagas">
                           <roleName type="title">mamʾǝr</roleName> Nagāš</persName>  
                              from <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC4432Mahdar">Māḫdara Māryām</placeName>.</note>
                          <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#20"/>
                           ወቅዱስኒ፡ ግሪኒንዲዎስ፡ ሶበ፡ ሰምዓ፡ ነገረ፡ ኤርባን፡ ተፈሥሐ፡ ወይቤ፡ ስማዕ፡ ኤርባን፡ ወለቡ፡ ዘከመ፡ እገብር፡ ለከ፡ ክርስቶስሃ፡ 
                           በገሃድኑ፡ አው፡ በራዕይ። ወአውሥአ፡ ወይቤ፡ ኤርባን፡ ኦአባ፡ ቅድመ፡ ዘነገርከኒ፡ ከመ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ወከመ፡ ክርስቶስኒ፡ ሀሎ፡ በሰማይ፡ 
                           ለይረድ፡ ወምስሌሁ፡ ንትናገር። ወዘንተ፡ ተአምረ፡ ነአምን፡ ወንጠመቅ፡ ወንትመሐል፡ መሐላ፡ ወከመዝ፡ ገብሩ፡ ወእምድኅረዝ፡ 
                           ተአምር፡ ዘኢአምኑ፡ ከመ፡ ይትመተሩ፡ በሰይፍ፡
                          </explicit>
                          <listBibl type="secondary">
                              <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/HNIPA5MV"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Ricci1949Nagran"/><title level="a">Una nuova narrazione amarico-geez de’ fatti di Nagran</title><title level="j">Annali dell'Istituto Orientale di Napoli</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Lanfranco</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Ricci</t:surname></author><date>1949</date><biblScope unit="page">417-429</biblScope></bibl>
                          </listBibl>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                          <locus from="30" to="110v"/>
                          <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7145MFTabiban">Maṣḥafa falāsfā ṭabibān</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ፈላስፋ፡ ጠቢባን፡ ዘተናገሩ፡ 
                              ባቲ፡ ለለ፩፩፡ እምኔሆሙ፡ በአምጣነ፡ ክሂሎቶሙ፡ ወናሁ፡ አስተጋብኡ፡ ውስቴታ፡ ነገረ፡ ምዕዳን፡ 
                              ብዙኃ<supplied reason="omitted">ት</supplied>፡ <choice>
                                  <sic>ወተገሣጸ፡</sic>
                                  <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ወተግሣጽ፡</corr>
                              </choice> ሠናያት፡ ወዜና፡ ቅሥምተ፡ ከመ፡ ፄው፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> 
                        <locus target="#32r"/> ይቤ፡ እንከ፡ እስመ፡ 
                              ዘያነብብ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አምላካዊት፡ ዘልፈ፡ 
                              ይረክብ፡ ረባሐ፡ እስመ፡ መጽሕፍትሰ፡ መካነ፡ መዝገበ፡ አእምሮ፡ ወጥበብ፡ እሙንቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ይቤ፡ ልዎ፡ ለመነኮስ፡ በእንተ፡ ምንትኑ፡ ኀደገ፡ 
                              ዓለመ፡ ይቤ፡ ጠየቁ፡ አነ፡ ከመ፡ አነ፡ እመጽእ፡ ምስሌሃ፡ እንበለ፡ ፈቃድከ፡ ወካዕበ፡ ይቤልዎ፡ 
                              ለመነኮስ፡ መኑ፡ ውእቱ፡ ኃዳጌ፡ ዓለም፡ ወመናኔ፡ ዓለም፡ ይቤ፡ ዘያመዘግን፡ በንዋይ፡ በኅዳጥ፡ እምነ፡ 
                              ሲሳይ፡ ወዘድልው፡ ዘልፈ፡ ለመዊት፡ ወይቤሎ፡ ለምንትኑ፡ ትለብስ፡ ሠቀ፡ ይቤ፡ ከመ፡ እትመሰሎሙ፡ 
                              ለሰብእ፡ ምኩራን፨
                          </incipit>
                          <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                              ይቤ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ፩እምጠቢባን፡ ሐመ፡ ደዌ፡ ጽኑዓ፡ በሕማመ፡ ከርሥ፡ ወሶበ፡ ቀርበ፡ ዕለተ፡ ሞቱ፡ 
                              ይቤልዎ፡ <choice>
                                  <sic>አርዳዊሁ፡</sic>
                                  <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">አርዳኢሁ፡</corr>
                              </choice> እስመ፡ ጠቢብ፡ አንተ፡ ዘትሁብ፡ ፈውሰ፡ ለኵሉ፡ እፎ፡ ዘይትፌወስ፡ ርእሰከ፡ ወእምዝ፡ 
                              አውጽአ፡ ማየ፡ ዘድልወቱ፡ ፻፡ 
                           <sic>ልጥረ፡</sic>
                           <sic>ወወድየ፡</sic>
                              ውስቴቱ፡ ፩፡ 
                           <sic>ድኅርመ፡</sic>
                         መድኃኒት፡ ወአይበሶ፡ ወኮነ፡ ከመ፡ ዕብን፡ 
                              ኢትሬእዩኑ፡ ዘከመ፡ አይበስኩ፡ 
                           <sic>በ፩ድሕርመ፡</sic>
                         መድኃኒት፡ ፻፡ <add place="above">ል</add>ጥረ፡ 
                              ማይ፡ ወእምይእዜሰ፡ በላዕኩ፡ <gap reason="illegible"/>ጥረ፡ 
                           <sic>መድኃኒት፡</sic>
                              ዘአይበሰ፡ ፩ልጥረ፡ ማይ፡ ወናሁ፡ ስዕ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ኩ፡ ፈውሶ፡ ሕማመ፡ 
                              ከርሥየ፡ በውእቱ፡ መድኃኒት፡ ወሶበ፡ በጽሐ፡ ለሰብእ፡ ጽኑዕ፡ ደዌ፡ 
                           <sic>ወኢቀረበ፡</sic>
                         
                              ዕለተ፡ ሞቱ፡ ይክል፡ ፈውሶቶ፡ መድኃኒት፡ ወሶበ፡ ቀርበ፡ ዕለተ፡ ሞቱ፡ ኢይክል፡ ፈውሶቶ፡ መስኃኒት፨
                          </explicit>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                          <locus from="110v" to="150"/>
                          <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7144MFTabiban">Maṣḥafa falāsfā ṭabibān</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሐሪ፡ ወመስተሣህል፡ ንወጥን፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ጠቢባን፡ ዘተናገሩ፡ ቦቱ፡ 
                              ለለ፩፩እምኔሆሙ፡ በአምጣነ፡ ክሂሎቶሙ፡ ይቤ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ወሬዛ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ይኄይስ፡ እምአረጋዊ፡ አብድ፡
                          </incipit>
                          <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                              ይቤ፡ ስቅራጥስ፡ ለአርዳኢሁ፡ ኩኑ፡ ድልዋነ፡ ለሞት፡ ለተዘክሮ፡ ከመ፡ ይፈድፍድ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ሕ</supplied>ይወትክሙ፡ 
                              ወዓዲ፡ ይቤሎሙ፡ ለእመ፡ ፈቀድክሙ፡ 
                           <sic>ትሕየው፡</sic>
                         በሠናይ፡ አኅፅፁ፡ አጥርዮ፡ 
                              ከመ፡ ይኅፅፅ፡ ትካዝክሙ፡ <del rend="expunctuated">ሰ</del>ዘሰ፡ <choice>
                                  <sic>ትውኀበ፡</sic>
                                  <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ተውኅበ፡</corr>
                              </choice> 
                           <sic>ጥብብ፡</sic>
                         ኢይኅዝን፡ በእንተ፡ ኃጢአ፡ ወርቅ፡ ወብሩር፡ 
                              አማኅፀንኩክሙ፡ ፍርህዎ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ወዕቀቡ፡ ትእዛዞ፡ ተፈጸመ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ጥበብ፡ ስብሐት፡ 
                              ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን።
                          </explicit>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                          <locus from="151r" to="161r"/>
                          <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4916PhysB">Zenā mǝssāleyāt za-ṭabib Fisǝʾalgos</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#151r"/>
                              ንጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ ድርሳነ፡ ዘፊስአልጎስ፡ ዘያሌቡ፡ ጥበበ፡ ለአእምሮ፡ 
                           <sic>ቀደማይ፡</sic>
                         ነገር፡ በእንተ፡ እንስሳ፡ ንወጥን፡
                              በእንተ፡ አንበሳ፡ ንጉሠ፡ አራዊት፡
                          </incipit>
                          <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#161r"/>
                              ሳሙኤል፡ ወኤርምያስ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡ ወኢሳይያስ፡
                          </explicit>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                          <locus target="#219v"/>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <title>Rose of the eight winds</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                          <locus from="220v" to="223v"/>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <title>Seven circular drawings for divinatory purposes</title>
                          <note>Each drawing consists of three circles subdivided by fourteen radii. Each section accommodates letters of 
                              the Ethiopian alphabet. The inner circles host short sentences related to Jesus Christ: <q xml:lang="gez">ሀሎ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡</q>, 
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ይቤዙ፡ አኃዊሁ፡</q>, <q xml:lang="gez">ይዋሂ፡ ፍጡራነ፡</q>, <q xml:lang="gez">ያድኅን፡ አዳምሃ፡</q>, <q xml:lang="gez">ይሄሉ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለም፡</q>,
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ህላዌሁ፡ ዘኢይትዓወቅ፡</q>, and <q xml:lang="gez">ኦሆ፡ ብሂሎ፡ መጽአ፡</q>.</note>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                          <locus target="#226"/>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7139HassabaFi">Five magic formulas</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#226"/>
